{"tid":2073560,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"初夏 －彩虹小隊致香港人公開信","createTime":"2020-06-21T12:08:10.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-21T13:27:29.000Z","uid":314210,"like":18,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"3fb6d47845862407821ace8862049fa07f423722","tid":2073560,"uid":314210,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-21T12:08:10.000Z","msg":"迎接初夏，一年過後「勇武」這兩字彷彿逐漸淡出人們的視線外。自反送中以來，香港人一直飽受著警暴等不公平待遇；哪裡有壓迫，哪裡就會有反抗。所謂「勇武」就在這此的社會壓力下誕生，一群又一群像我們這樣的香港人，決心走上街。<br />\n<br />\n我們曾經是被社會唾棄的一群，被扣上「暴力」，「暴徒」等等帽子，甚至被割席。但記得，「是你教會我們和平遊行是沒有用的」；在香港人一次又一次經歷過惡夢般的待遇， 「721」，「831」，甚至一條又一條生命離開我們的時候，我們才驚醒，已經回不去了。政權的打擊是迫使我們醒覺，我們終於站在了一起，「不割席，不分化；兄弟爬山，各自努力」，勇武開始壯大，社會開始接受，勇武抗爭或者會是一條出路。<br />\n<br />\n「中大保衛戰」，「理大圍城」等一幕又一幕的畫面，都象徵着我們「和勇不分」的精神，我們之間沒有分彼此，只憑着一句簡單的「手足」稱呼着對方，「和理非」和「勇武」站到一起，抵抗著暴政對港人的侵犯。無奈的是，在武力不對等，「捉鬼」文化的情況下，我們承認無論在士氣上或是精神上，對我們都是一種打擊。我們當中被捕的被捕，流亡海外的要流亡海外，在腐敗的政權打壓下，我們失去了一位一位的手足。<br />\n<br />\n或者我們不得不承認「勇武」抗爭某程度上或許去到了一個樽頸的位置，但這不代表我們放棄了，只要香港需要我們，我們一直都在。同樣地我們認為「勇武」是一種心態，只要你有和極權抗爭的勇氣和意志，你，我，他， 我們每一個都是「勇武」。致香港人，一息尚存，抗爭到底，直至光復香港，我們煲底相聚。<br />\n<br />\n初夏到了，我們會回來的。<br />\n<br />\n彩虹小隊上<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.thestandnews.com/politics/%E5%88%9D%E5%A4%8F-%E5%BD%A9%E8%99%B9%E5%B0%8F%E9%9A%8A%E8%87%B4%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E4%BA%BA%E5%85%AC%E9%96%8B%E4%BF%A1/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E5%2588%259D%25E5%25A4%258F-%25E5%25BD%25A9%25E8%2599%25B9%25E5%25B0%258F%25E9%259A%258A%25E8%2587%25B4%25E9%25A6%2599%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E5%2585%25AC%25E9%2596%258B%25E4%25BF%25A1%2F&d=CgUtGs1XjGBKDnLe79D2Yy8EbckYnMoWLUJTUpLSOd8%3D&h=cc096ff2\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E5%2588%259D%25E5%25A4%258F-%25E5%25BD%25A9%25E8%2599%25B9%25E5%25B0%258F%25E9%259A%258A%25E8%2587%25B4%25E9%25A6%2599%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E5%2585%25AC%25E9%2596%258B%25E4%25BF%25A1%2F&h=d846a405\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.thestandnews.com/politics/%E5%88%9D%E5%A4%8F-%E5%BD%A9%E8%99%B9%E5%B0%8F%E9%9A%8A%E8%87%B4%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E4%BA%BA%E5%85%AC%E9%96%8B%E4%BF%A1/</a>"},{"pid":"512a8acfa2d8f6bce4fb7c4721aefad365121046","tid":2073560,"uid":202137,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-21T12:11:34.000Z","msg":"點彩虹法？成隊人都LGBTQQIDAAPPO2SBNBGNCGGAPPO+?"},{"pid":"f2f5a1f5f60dfed4344201a3992b29efed9d05b6","tid":2073560,"uid":261544,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-21T12:13:46.000Z","msg":"又釣到五毛一隻<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nBtw, respect 各勇武手足<br />\n我地會係煲底見嘅"},{"pid":"06514ee580637d2cc926e4c66fdd8530ff43fc49","tid":2073560,"uid":72654,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-21T12:15:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"83b9061a64a525f40476ef4bfe51e1dcdb7a9da6","tid":2073560,"uid":13644,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-21T12:17:54.000Z","msg":"多謝手足<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"74bb01f7a5c2ceedbb3634b2d3fae4df77065f84","tid":2073560,"uid":298893,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-21T12:18:18.000Z","msg":"做的不需說，說的不會做!<br />\n<br />\n手足，煲底見"},{"pid":"e52712692c401e784a57faebc99bc0bbd6c8ba30","tid":2073560,"uid":98232,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-21T12:20:42.000Z","msg":"我地雲影風小隊全體向彩虹小隊致敬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f66bb5dab48c6478d148e84681a8df803bcd5ac5","tid":2073560,"uid":314210,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-21T12:25:4